 How to use?
 
 	First, you need to "enable" the font. You can add these lignes in your .xinitrc
-		xset +fp /usr/share/fonts/envypn
+		xset +fp @PREFIX@/lib/X11/fonts/envypn
 		xset fp rehash
 
 	Restart X and now you can preview the font with xfontsel or xfd.
